====== H6677: צַוָּאר ======

===== Source =====

or   ; (Nehemiah 3:5), or   ; (Song of Solomon 4:9), or (feminine)   ; (Micah 2:3), intensively from  H6696  in the sense of  ;

===== Meaning =====

binding the back of the  neck  (as that on which burdens are  bound )

===== Definitions =====

  - binding
  - neck
  - bound

===== Usage =====

neck.
